collection.name: Zoofrenz by Zombot Studio
collection.description:
You can now awaken your Apefrenz!

We're migrating to the 2.0 collection 我們搬家到新的2.0收藏 : https://opensea.io/collection/zoofrenz-apefrenz-2-0

Migration can be done via 從這裡遷移你的1.0 -> 2.0  : https://www.zoofrenz.com/migrate

A future-proofed metaverse IP built by veteran game designers and artists. 
Zoofrenz begins with a collection of 6,666 Apefrenz avatars that generate $FRENSHIP utility tokens.
$FRENSHIP can be used to redeem various additional NFTs in our ecosystem.

1.  Float Tanks - 4000 Float tanks allow you to transform your existing Apefrenz to an Awakened Apefrenz with a set of brand new traits.
2.  First Class Zoo Pass - 666 passes that grant exclusive access to physical perks and events.
3. 3D Avatar Pass - Every Apefrenz can ascend into metaverse-ready 3D playable characters.
$FRENSHIP token checker:
https://www.zoofrenz.com/search

由資深遊戲設計團隊Zombot Studio打造的元宇宙 IP。 Zoofrenz 以 6,666 個 Apefrenz NFT 開始，Apefrenz後續可以覺醒成元宇宙裡的 3D Playable Character NFT。 元宇宙的未來，現在就觸手可及。你也準備好覺醒了嗎？
